actual.comment:
1. First Chapter of BUR (National Circumstances) finalized;
2.  In partnership with Environmental Information and Education Center of the Ministry of Environment and Natural Resource Protection of Georgia GHG Inventory for 2012-2013 is underway as well as updating of 2010-2011 GHG inventory is being prepared; Quality Assurance/Quality Check on GHG emission inventory is in progress;
3. Preparation of Mitigation and Constraints&Gaps Chapters of BUR is underway;
4.  MRV experts being recruited;

1. Joint flood recovery needs assessment conducted jointly with the WB and the Government;
Findings and recommendations presented to the Government and stakeholders, including on enhancing of DRR system on Municipal level;
Coordination of actions ensured though several stakeholder coordination meetings;
Recovery Needs Assessment Report developed;
2. Development of Recovery Framework ongoing;
